          "text": "（高行周上。院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鹤发童颜，两鬓斑然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾记当年摆战场，五虎二龙逼彦章。兴兵打仗谁敢挡，保定刘王锦家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫，高行周，绰号鹞子。刘主驾前为臣，官拜东鲁王之职，这也不在话下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因昨晚三更，偶得一梦，梦见红脸大汉，手执大刀前来行刺。你看今晚明星"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朗朗，不免到观星台上，观看本命星辰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子、院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯观星台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。想当初老夫在狗家滩摆战场之时，前发不过齐眉，后发不过雁尾，到今"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝两鬓苍然。光阴，光阴，你走得快不快也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "黄巢起义灭大唐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高行周",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "沙陀搬来李晋王。"
